this_title: Don Henley: The End of the Innocence
introduction: Don Henley performs in the music video "The End of the Innocence" from the album "The End of the Innocence" recorded for Geffen Records. Don Henley sings in the black and white video while clips show the coming of age of a young man through the years. Shots feature a youth play with siblings, a man with his girlfriend, a man in the military, and the remains of a ticker-tape parade.
